Description: Converts auto-changelog CHANGELOG.md to debian/changelog format
 This package provides a script that converts a CHANGELOG.md file generated by
 auto-changelog into the debian/changelog format required for Debian packaging.
 .
 It extracts version information, release dates, and change details to create
 a properly formatted changelog for Debian packages.
